      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 42:5">Zab 42:5</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 61:10">Isa 61:10</ref></char>
    </note> Walakini nitamfurahia BWANA,</para>
  <para style="q" vid="HAB 3:18">Nitamshangilia Mungu wa wokovu wangu.<verse eid="HAB 3:18" /></para>
  <para style="q">
